These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different games are played: domino, poker, mah-jongg, canasta, chess, billiard, whist
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, january, november, october, may, september, april
7 different pets are kept: rabbit, hedgehog, ferret, chinchilla, hamster, bird, turtle
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the owner of the ferret##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the person playing poker is the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the person who's birthday is in september##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is the person playing chess##1
12. the person playing chess is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
14. the person who's birthday is in september is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
16. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
17. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
18. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
19. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Game      | poker  | billiard        | chess | mah-jongg      | canasta     | domino      | whist     |
| Birthday   | january | october         | april   | july | september    | may | november |
| Pet         | ferret | hamster | rabbit | hedgehog | turtle  | bird  | chinchilla    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

