 2. the photographer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the bartender##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 6. the dancer is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is the writer##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the dancer##1
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's birthday is in february##2
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's birthday is in january##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
13. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's hobby is singing##2
14. the writer is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
17. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the manager##1
18. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
19. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
20. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person driving the ship and the person who's birthday is in september##2

